data.description: Vintage charm meets modern design in this 1926 Midtown marvel. The home has 3 bedrooms, 3 full baths, spacious living & dining rooms and a great backyard & entertaining space w/a pool. Hardwood floors, new carpet upstairs, new AC unit upstairs, garage & carport, privacy fence, dog run. Large kitchen space w/great flow to dining & living rooms. Great front porch, excellent neighborhood, close to TU, grocery store, expressway and walkable to shops, dining, university, and fairgrounds. This home has an assumable loan with a 3.75% interest rate. Qualified buyer can take over the seller's locked in rate and loan terms. Please ask for details.
